---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import ExampleEmbed from '../../../components/ExampleEmbed.astro';
import { kraftSidebar } from '../../../data/kraft-sidebar';
import { Code } from 'astro:components';
import {kraftLiveExamples, githubRepo} from '../../../data/site';
---

<DocsLayout title="SemanticUI DSL" sidebar={kraftSidebar} description="A fluent Kotlin DSL for building FomanticUI interfaces in Kraft">

<h1>SemanticUI DSL</h1>

<p class="text-xl text-gray-400 !mt-2 !mb-8">
  A fluent, type-safe Kotlin DSL for the <a href="https://fomantic-ui.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FomanticUI</a> CSS framework.
  Write <code>ui.blue.button</code> instead of <code>class="ui blue button"</code>.
</p>

<h2>How it works</h2>

<p>The DSL starts with <code>ui</code> (or <code>noui</code> for non-UI classes) and chains modifiers using Kotlin properties:</p>

<Code code={`// This:
ui.inverted.blue.segment {
    ui.header H2 { +"Welcome" }
    ui.basic.button { +"Click me" }
}

// Generates this HTML:
// <div class="ui inverted blue segment">
//   <h2 class="ui header">Welcome</h2>
//   <button class="ui basic button">Click me</button>
// </div>`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<p>Every modifier is a Kotlin property that adds a CSS class. The final call (<code>segment &#123;&#125;</code>, <code>button &#123;&#125;</code>, <code>header H2 &#123;&#125;</code>) creates the HTML element and opens a block for its children.</p>

<h2>Core elements</h2>

<h3>Buttons</h3>

<Code code={`ui.button { +"Default" }
ui.blue.button { +"Blue" }
ui.basic.green.button { +"Outlined green" }
ui.icon.button { icon.heart() }
ui.labeled.icon.button { icon.download(); +"Download" }

// Button group
ui.buttons {
    ui.button { +"One" }
    ui.button { +"Two" }
    ui.button { +"Three" }
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h3>Segments</h3>

<Code code={`ui.segment { +"Basic segment" }
ui.raised.segment { +"Raised" }
ui.padded.segment { +"Extra padding" }
ui.inverted.segment { +"Dark background" }
ui.placeholder.segment { +"Empty state placeholder" }

// Stacked segments
ui.segments {
    ui.segment { +"First" }
    ui.segment { +"Second" }
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h3>Headers</h3>

<Code code={`ui.header H1 { +"Page title" }
ui.header H2 { +"Section header" }
ui.sub.header { +"Sub-header" }
ui.icon.header {
    icon.settings()
    noui.content { +"Settings" }
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h3>Grid system</h3>

<Code code={`ui.two.column.grid {
    noui.column {
        +"Left column"
    }
    noui.column {
        +"Right column"
    }
}

// Responsive
ui.four.column.doubling.stackable.grid {
    noui.column { +"A" }
    noui.column { +"B" }
    noui.column { +"C" }
    noui.column { +"D" }
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h3>Cards</h3>

<Code code={`ui.three.cards {
    noui.card {
        noui.content {
            ui.header { +"Card title" }
            noui.description { +"Card content" }
        }
        noui.extra.content {
            icon.user()
            +"4 members"
        }
    }
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h3>Labels</h3>

<Code code={`ui.label { +"Default" }
ui.red.label { +"Error" }
ui.green.label { +"Success" }
ui.circular.blue.label { +"42" }`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h3>Menus</h3>

<Code code={`ui.vertical.inverted.menu {
    noui.item A {
        onClick { evt -> router.navToUri(evt, Nav.home()) }
        +"Home"
    }
    noui.item A {
        onClick { evt -> router.navToUri(evt, Nav.about()) }
        +"About"
    }
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h3>Tables</h3>

<Code code={`ui.celled.table Table {
    thead {
        tr {
            th { +"Name" }
            th { +"Status" }
        }
    }
    tbody {
        users.forEach { user ->
            tr {
                td { +user.name }
                td { ui.green.label { +"Active" } }
            }
        }
    }
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h2>Conditional styling</h2>

<p>The <code>given()</code> modifier applies styles based on a condition:</p>

<Code code={`// Disable button when form is invalid
ui.blue.button.given(!isValid) { disabled }.then {
    onClick { submit() }
    +"Submit"
}

// Highlight active menu item
ui.item.given(isActive) { active }.then A {
    +"Dashboard"
}

// Add loading state
ui.button.given(isLoading) { loading }.then {
    +"Save"
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<p><strong>How it reads:</strong> "A blue button, given it's not valid, make it disabled, then render it."</p>

<h2>Colors</h2>

<p>16 named colors plus brand colors:</p>

<Code code={`ui.red.label { +"Red" }
ui.orange.label { +"Orange" }
ui.yellow.label { +"Yellow" }
ui.olive.label { +"Olive" }
ui.green.label { +"Green" }
ui.teal.label { +"Teal" }
ui.blue.label { +"Blue" }
ui.violet.label { +"Violet" }
ui.purple.label { +"Purple" }
ui.pink.label { +"Pink" }
ui.brown.label { +"Brown" }
ui.grey.label { +"Grey" }
ui.black.label { +"Black" }
ui.white.label { +"White" }`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h2>Sizes</h2>

<Code code={`ui.mini.button { +"Mini" }
ui.tiny.button { +"Tiny" }
ui.small.button { +"Small" }
ui.medium.button { +"Medium" }
ui.large.button { +"Large" }
ui.big.button { +"Big" }
ui.huge.button { +"Huge" }
ui.massive.button { +"Massive" }`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h2>Icons</h2>

<p>FomanticUI includes Font Awesome icons:</p>

<Code code={`icon.home()
icon.user()
icon.search()
icon.trash()
icon.check_circle()
icon.exclamation_circle()
icon.sign_out_alternate()
icon.grip_vertical()
icon.eraser()
icon.dollar_sign()
icon.heart()
icon.settings()
icon.download()`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h2>Modals</h2>

<Code code={`ui.button {
    onClick {
        modals.show { handle ->
            OkCancelModal {
                mini(
                    handle = handle,
                    header = { ui.header { +"Confirm" } },
                    content = {
                        ui.content {
                            +"Are you sure you want to delete this?"
                        }
                    },
                ) { result ->
                    when (result) {
                        OkCancelModal.Result.Ok -> deleteItem()
                        OkCancelModal.Result.Cancel -> { /* do nothing */ }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
    +"Delete"
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<p>Modal sizes: <code>mini()</code>, <code>tiny()</code>, <code>small()</code>, <code>large()</code>, and full-size.</p>

<h2>Toast notifications</h2>

<Code code={`// Info toast
toasts.info("Settings saved successfully")

// Warning
toasts.warning("Your session expires in 5 minutes")

// Error
toasts.error("Failed to save changes")

// Random type
toasts.append(Message.Type.entries.random(), "Some message")`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h2>Context menus and popups</h2>

<Code code={`// Context menu on right-click
ui.segment {
    onContextMenuStoppingEvent { evt ->
        popups.showContextMenu(evt, PopupsManager.Positioning.BottomLeft) {
            ui.vertical.menu {
                noui.item { +"Copy" }
                noui.item { +"Paste" }
                noui.item { +"Delete" }
            }
        }
    }
    +"Right-click me"
}

// Hover popup
ui.button {
    popups.showHoverPopup.topLeft(tag = this) {
        +"This is a tooltip"
    }
    +"Hover me"
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

<h2>Custom CSS</h2>

<p>Combine the DSL with inline CSS when needed:</p>

<Code code={`div {
    css {
        marginTop = 16.px
        marginLeft = 250.px
        width = 100.pct
        height = 50.vh
    }
    +"Styled content"
}`} lang="kotlin" theme="vitesse-dark" />

    <h2>See it in action</h2>

    <p>The full SemanticUI component showcase — buttons, cards, menus, tables, grids, and more:</p>

    <ExampleEmbed
            src={`${kraftLiveExamples.fomanticui}#/elements/button`}
            title="Kraft SemanticUI Components"
            height="800px"
            sourceUrl={`${githubRepo}/tree/master/kraft/examples/fomanticui/src/jsMain/kotlin/pages`}
    />

    <div class="not-prose mt-8 flex gap-4">
  <a href="/ultra/kraft/addons" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-500 transition-colors">
    Addons &rarr;
  </a>
</div>

</DocsLayout>
